<h1 id="makers-agency-landing-page">Makers Agency Landing Page</h1>

<p>An experiment in Landing Pages to see if there's interest in a proposition we're thinking of trying out.</p>

<p>From an original Codrops demo, outlined below.</p>

<h3 id="the-codrops-demo">The Codrops demo</h3>

<p>A tutorial on how to use fragment shaders in WebGL to create an animated heat haze distortion effect on images and text.</p>

<p><a href="http://tympanus.net/codrops/?p=26950">Article on Codrops</a></p>

